com.bixlabs.bkotlin

Class Validator

  • com.bixlabs.bkotlin.Validator

  • public class Validator

    Minimum chainable validation utilities.

Usage example:

var result: Boolean = editText.validator()
      .email()
      .atLeastOneUpperCase()
      .atLeastOneLowerCase()
      .maximumLength(20)
      .minimumLength(5)
      .noNumbers()
      .validate()
